description: Retrieves information about the specified association between a service network and a service.

parameters.name: serviceNetworkServiceAssociationIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID or ARN of the association.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the association.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the association was created, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: createdBy
nested_items.description: The account that created the association.

nested_items.name: customDomainName
nested_items.description: The custom domain name of the service.

nested_items.name: domainName
nested_items.description: The domain name of the service.

nested_items.name: hostedZoneId
nested_items.description: The ID of the hosted zone.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the service network and service association.

nested_items.name: serviceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service network.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkId
nested_items.description: The ID of the service network.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkName
nested_items.description: The name of the service network.
